扮演伏地魔</a>。</p><p>自9月份以来， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-fans-want-actor-to-play-voldemort-in-new-harry-potter-tv-series-3794443">球迷一直在讨论</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><i>Oppenheimer</i></a>明星的可能性，而Fiennes和Fiennes在最近认可的墨菲（Murphy）的原始电影中扮演了来自<i>Harry Potter的小人和《 Goblet of The Goblet》</i> 。</p><p>最近还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/j-k-rowling-remains-fairly-involved-in-harry-potter-tv-series-despite-fan-backlash-to-anti-trans-statements-3812282">证实，罗琳仍然“相当参与”</a>即将推出的系列，尽管她过去有反跨性别情绪，而且许多粉丝<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/harry-potter-fans-arent-happy-that-j-k-rowling-is-involved-with-new-tv-series-3769148">之前反对她的参与</a>。</p><p>本周早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/harry-potter-tv-series-has-been-delayed-until-2027-3818883">还确认该系列已被推迟到2027年</a>。</p><p> Papa <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/paapa-essiedu-in-talks-to-play-severus-snape-in-harry-potter-tv-series-but-some-fans-arent-convinced-3819105">Paapa Essiedu在“ Harry Potter”电视连续剧中扮演Severus Snape的会谈中，但有些粉丝并没有确信</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
